                     int victimAge,

Add incidentInformation in the system

Precondition:
description is the description of the incident localisation is the location of the incident, textually represented victimAge is the age of the victim (victimAge > 0) victimPregnant is the pregnancy of the victim
Postcondition
a new incident information is now stored in the database
